  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Christopher Dowswell was aide-de-camp to Nobel Laureate Dr. Norman E. Borlaug for more than 30 years. He joined the Sasakawa Africa Association (SAA) in 1991 and was appointed joint Executive Director in 2009. Chris worked tirelessly for SAA&apos;s objective of supporting smallholder farmers and particularly agricultural extension.  The Fund provides scholarships for degree training in Agricultural Extension, especially for women.</narrative>
